                Regulations.</content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1573023679910_002" name="2" temporalId="s1_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><sourceNote>(Omitted as spent—<ref href="/hk/2023/er2">E.R. 2 of
                2023</ref>)</sourceNote></subsection></section><section id="ID_1438403133117_002" name="s2" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2023-07-20" status="operational" temporalId="s2"><num value="2">2.</num><heading>Interpretation</heading><leadIn>In these regulations, unless the context otherwise requires—</leadIn><def name="GrossFloorArea"><term>gross
                floor
            area</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">總樓面面積</term>) means the floor area contained within the
            external walls of the building measured at each floor level (including any floor below
            the level of the ground, and any roof used for club purposes), together with the area of
            each balcony in the building, which shall be calculated from the overall dimensions of
            the balcony (including the thickness of the sides thereof), and the thickness of the
            external walls of the building.</def></section><section id="ID_1438403133133_001" name="s3" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2023-07-20" status="operational" temporalId="s3"><num value="3">3.</num><heading>Fee payable for the issue or renewal of certificate of exemption</heading><leadIn>The fee payable for the issue of a certificate of exemption under <ref>section 5(2)(b)</ref> or the renewal of a certificate of exemption under <ref>section 6(2)</ref> of the Ordinance shall be calculated according to the period of validity of the certificate as follows—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438412338144_012" name="a" temporalId="s3_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>for a period of 12
                months—$720;</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438412338144_020" name="b" temporalId="s3_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>for any other
                period—one-twelfth
                of $720 multiplied by the number of months for which the certificate is issued or
                renewed, as the case may be.</content></paragraph><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1993/ln449">L.N. 449 of 1993</ref>; <ref href="/hk/1994/ln623">L.N. 623 of 1994</ref>; <ref href="/hk/1996/ln16">L.N. 16 of 1996</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438403133133_003" name="s4" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2023-07-20" status="operational" temporalId="s4"><num value="4">4.</num><heading>Fee payable for the issue or renewal of certificate of compliance</heading><content>The fee payable for the issue of a certificate of compliance under <ref>section
